msgctxt "an4.222:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.222:0.2"
msgid "23. Duccaritavagga "
msgstr "23. Bad Conduct "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: paṭhamabāla-paṇḍitasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.222:0.3"
msgid "222. Diṭṭhisutta "
msgstr "222. View "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.222:1.1"
msgid "“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bālo abyatto asappuriso khataṃ upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo viññūnaṃ; bahuñca apuññaṃ pasavati. "
msgstr "“When a foolish, incompetent bad person has four qualities they keep themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and criticized by sensible people, and they make much bad karma. "

msgctxt "an4.222:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.222:1.3"
msgid "Kāyaduccaritena, vacīduccaritena, manoduccaritena, micchādiṭṭhiyā—"
msgstr "Bad conduct by way of body, speech, and mind, and wrong view. "

msgctxt "an4.222:1.4"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato bālo abyatto asappuriso khataṃ upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo viññūnaṃ, bahuñca apuññaṃ pasavati. "
msgstr "When a foolish, incompetent bad person has these four qualities they keep themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and criticized by sensible people, and they make much bad karma. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.222:2.1"
msgid "Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo viññūnaṃ, bahuñca puññaṃ pasavati. "
msgstr "When an astute, competent good person has four qualities they keep themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and criticized by sensible people, and they make much merit. "

msgctxt "an4.222:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.222:2.3"
msgid "Kāyasucaritena, vacīsucaritena, manosucaritena, sammādiṭṭhiyā—"
msgstr "Good conduct by way of body, speech, and mind, and right view. "

msgctxt "an4.222:2.4"
msgid "imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo viññūnaṃ; bahuñca puññaṃ pasavatī”ti. "
msgstr "When an astute, competent good person has these four qualities they keep themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and criticized by sensible people, and they make much merit.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.222:2.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

